                 <p><span><strong>Lifeability</strong> measures an individuals internal capacity to be happy and satisfied and his or her adeptness at taking advantage of the external environment.</span></p>\r\n                    </header>\r\n                    <article class="large-8 large-offset-1 medium-8 medium-offset-1 small-12 columns">\r\n                        [wp-simple-survey-1]\r\n                    </article>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </section>\r\n        </div>', 'Your Quality of Life Measures', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'your-quality-of-life-measures', '', '', '2016-02-11 20:30:00', '2016-02-11 20:30:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/life-measures-wordpress/?page_id=234', 0, 'page', '', 0),
